# Dev-only one-shot scripts — never committed.
#
# Runtime probes that forge authenticated JWTs against a Supabase project
# (apps/api/scripts/probe-*.ts) bundle SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET-driven token
# generation in a single file. The secret itself is the vulnerability
# vector — but a committed forging utility lowers the bar for an insider
# or supply-chain attacker who later obtains the secret. Keep them local.
#
# Dev DDL one-shots (apps/workers/scripts/dev-*.mjs) execute DROP/CREATE
# against whatever DATABASE_URL is set in the environment with no guard.
# A mis-set env var would drop production schema objects on invocation.
# Keep them local; migrations are the source of truth.
apps/api/scripts/probe-*.ts
apps/workers/scripts/dev-*.mjs
